        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer278676216" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14729965629614606665">If I had read The Courage To Be years ago when I bought it, I would have given it five stars. It is cerebral and insightful and at the time I was into such books - I was reading Erich Fromm, Kierkegaard, et.al. But I have taken up Zen Buddhism since then and I found TCTB too abstract and cerebral for my present tastes. It is a fine book to occupy your mind, but it did not encourage my heart or transform my being.</span>

