        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3536410874" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11089269146309476042">I felt that this is a great book. I read it once when I was in the army getting ready to deploy to Iraq and I found it very helpful. Now I am a little bit older, married, trying to conceive, and struggling with the effects of PTSD and discrimination, and I still find this book just as meaningful. It can be very abstruse and you have to take it slowly and ponder it for a while.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


